📄 P.07 – Document Parser

An AI-powered document parser and chatbot for PDF and Excel files.
Upload your files, process them, and interact with their contents through a conversational interface.

✨ Features

📑 Extract text from PDF files using pypdf
📊 Parse and analyze Excel files with pandas
🤖 Chat with your documents using LangChain + Ollama (LLaMA2)
🎨 Clean and interactive Streamlit frontend with sidebar + chatbot UI
⚡ Simple workflow: Upload → Process → Ask

🛠️ Tech Stack

Backend AI: LangChain + Ollama (LLaMA2)
PDF Parsing: pypdf
Excel Parsing: pandas
Frontend: Streamlit

MODEL=llama2
-Pull the Ollama model
   ollama pull llama2
-Run the frontend
   streamlit run app.py

🚀 Usage
Launch the Streamlit app (link shown in terminal).
Upload your PDF/Excel documents from the sidebar.
Click Process Document.
Start asking questions about your data!

📌 Example Use Cases
🔍 Search through research papers
📊 Analyze Excel reports quickly
📚 Summarize lengthy documents
🧑‍💻 Build personal AI-powered knowledge assistants



